/BLCHHv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FBLCHHv&d=9wUuuD4EdXwN53T3OcOytW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=78df1d75\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/BLCHHv</a>"},{"pid":"b60e42a481461ae02ca2d84db04aa3b271d1a09f","tid":340920,"uid":91990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"更新：第六回[url]《綁匪的索求》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/y1U2hS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fy1U2hS&d=9wUuuD4EdXwN53T3OcOytW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5dcf54e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/y1U2hS</a><br />\n<br />\n小林正雪和美女刑警周嫣終於想到辦法調查那神秘的大宅。另一方面，報案人收到了來自綁匪的進一步要求⋯⋯"},{"pid":"3e05c233c2ec8962eafa3a49fdd68d64974975ef","tid":340920,"uid":91990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"更新第七回：《自由的人》<br />\n<br />\n特首千金綁架案的故事，已近尾聲了。人質獲釋，失踪的市民也尋回了，但是綁匪卻逍遙法外。小林正雪心有不甘，誓要尋找事件的真相⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/nsDzVw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnsDzVw&d=9wUuuD4EdXwN53T3OcOytW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=bdb57640\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/nsDzVw</a>"},{"pid":"fb0b96f413b60026a69dcf99f9c38ab90c80962f","tid":340920,"uid":91990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"這個故事的構思是根據香港現時的情況。這個看似自由的城市，暗裡正在慢慢地變化，某些擁有特權的階級，不但比平民百姓「更自由」，且能剝奪別人的自由。警察作為執法者，應該如何自處？"}]}